	<div class="g-bg-secondary g-pa-50">
		<h3 class="g-mb-25">Want to talk to someone?</h3>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6 g-mb-30 g-mb-0--md">
				<h3 class="h5 mb-3">10-5 Eastern Customer Support:</h3>
				<div class="mb-3">
					<a class="g-color-main g-color-primary--hover g-font-size-13" href="http://support.aoblockchain.io" target="_blank">Support Site</a>
					<span class="g-mx-15">|</span>
					<a class="g-color-main g-color-primary--hover g-font-size-13" href="mailto:info@aoblockchain.io">info@aoblockchain.io</a>
				</div>
				<p class="g-font-size-12">Our Support and Investor Relations chats are currently staffed by our CTO and CEO, so we can provide the quickest, most accurate answers to interested parties.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Chat with Us</h3>
				<div class="mb-3">
					<a class="g-color-main g-color-primary--hover g-font-size-13 investChat" href="#">Investor Relations</a>
