				</div>
				<div class="mb-3">
					<a class="g-color-main g-color-primary--hover g-font-size-13 supportChat" href="#">Support</a>
					<span class="g-color-text g-font-size-13">(from 08.00 AM to 06.00 PM)</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
